<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<title>Security TOTP - Google Authenticator Compatibility Demo</title>
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
		<!-- Bootstrap -->
		<link href="${request}/resources/css/bootstrap.css" rel="stylesheet" media="screen">
		<link href="${request}/resources/css/theme.css" rel="stylesheet" media="screen">		
		<!-- HTML5 shim and Respond.js IE8 support of HTML5 elements and media queries -->
		<!--[if lt IE 9]>
		<script src="${request}/resources/js/html5shiv.js"></script>
		<script src="${request}/resources/js/respond.min.js"></script>
		<![endif]-->
		<!-- jQuery (necessary for Bootstrap's JavaScript plugins) -->
		<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery.js"></script>
		<script src="${request}/resources/js/totp.js"></script>
		#if (!$isLocalhost)
		<script>
		(function(i,s,o,g,r,a,m){i['GoogleAnalyticsObject']=r;i[r]=i[r]||function(){
		(i[r].q=i[r].q||[]).push(arguments)},i[r].l=1*new Date();a=s.createElement(o),
		m=s.getElementsByTagName(o)[0];a.async=1;a.src=g;m.parentNode.insertBefore(a,m)
		})(window,document,'script','//www.google-analytics.com/analytics.js','ga');
		
		ga('create', 'UA-47277867-1', 'security-totp.appspot.com');
		ga('send', 'pageview');
		</script>
		#end
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="container">
			<header>
			<h1>Security TOTP - Google Authenticator Compatibility Demo</h1>
			</header>
			<section>
				<div class="alert alert-warning">
					<p>This is only <strong>demo site</strong> and requires enabled cookies and HTML5 compatibile browser. It is never safe to transfer TOTP secret via <strong>unsecured protocol</strong> or store it in <strong>usecured cookie</strong> in user's browser!</p>
					<p>Generated TOTP is stored in a browser's cookie for 7 days if not refreshed. This website should not be used for authentication to real services.
					<br>Author do not takes responsibilities for any damages.</p>
				</div>
				<div id="wrapper"></div>
				<script type="text/template" id="template">
				<div class="row">
					<div class="col-md-4 col-lg-4">
						<div class="panel panel-default">
							<div class="panel-heading">
								<h2>Scan QR</h2>
							</div>
							<div class="panel-body">
								<img src="{{qr}}" alt="Scan QR">
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="col-md-4 col-lg-4">
						<div class="panel panel-default">
							<div class="panel-heading">
								<h2>Manual entry</h2>
							</div>
							<div class="panel-body">
								<p>Account: {{username}}
								<br>Host: {{host}}
								<br>Key: {{secret}}
								<br>Time Based: true
								##<br>Valid until: {{validUntil}}
								</p>
								<p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="${request}/totp/refresh" id="refresh">Refresh TOTP</a> <a class="btn btn-warning" href="${request}/totp/destroy" id="destroy">Destroy TOTP</a></p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="col-md-4 col-lg-4">
						<div class="panel panel-default">
							<div class="panel-heading">
								<h2>Verify TOTP</h2>
							</div>
							<div class="panel-body">
								<form method="post" action="${request}/totp/verify" id="verify">
									<div class="form-group">
										<label>Code</label>
										<input type="text" name="code" maxlength="6" class="form-control">
									</div>
									<p><button type="submit" class="btn btn-success">Verify!</button></p>
								</form>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				</script>
				<div class="row">
					<div class="col-md-4 col-lg-4">
						<div class="panel panel-default">
							<div class="panel-heading">
								<h2>Generate TOTP</h2>
							</div>
							<div class="panel-body">
								<form method="post" action="${request}/totp/generate" id="generate">
									<div class="form-group">
										<label>Username</label> 
										<input type="text" name="username" class="form-control">
									</div>
									<p><button type="submit" class="btn btn-success">Generate!</button></p>
								</form>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="col-md-4 col-lg-4">
						<div class="panel panel-info">
							<div class="panel-heading">
								<h2>Google Authenticator</h2>
							</div>
							<div class="panel-body">
								<p>You can test generated security codes by using Google Authenticator. Guide how to install the application can be found at <a href="https://support.google.com/accounts/answer/1066447?hl=en" target="_blank">Google Help</a>.</p>
								<p>If you will follow the guide use generated barcode or information for manual data entry.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="col-md-4 col-lg-4 box">
						<div class="panel panel-primary	">
							<div class="panel-heading">
								<h2>Download</h2>
							</div>
							<div class="panel-body">
								<p>Source code for checkout and usage installation instructions available at <a href="https://github.com/hrax/security-totp">github</a>.</p>
								<p>Demo page sources available at <a href="https://github.com/hrax/security-totp/tree/security-totp-demo">github</a> as well.</p>
								<p><strong>Maven repository is being prepared.</strong></p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
			<footer>
				<small>by <a href="http://www.elepha.info">Gregor &quot;hrax&quot; Magdolen</a>, 2014, built with <a href="http://www.getbootstrap.com">Bootstrap</a></small>
			</footer>
			<script type="text/javascript">
			$(document).ready(function() {
				var totp = new TOTP('#template', '#wrapper');
				#if (${secret})
				totp.show({
					"qr": "${qr}",
					"username": "${username}",
					"host": "${host}",
					"secret": "${secret}"
				});
				#end
				totp.attach();
			});
			</script>
		</div>
	</body>
<html>
